{
  "name": "Shocking Grasp",
  "type": "spell",
  "_id": "matSplShockingGr",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Lightning springs from your hand to deliver a shock to a creature you touch. The creature must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or take [[/damage 1d8 lightning]] damage and cannot take reactions until the start of its next turn. If the creature succeeds on the saving throw it takes no damage, but cannot take opportunity attacks against you until the end of your turn.</p><p><strong>Cantrip Upgrade.</strong> The damage increases by 1d8 when you reach levels 5 ([[/damage 2d8 lightning]]), 11 ([[/damage 3d8 lightning]]), and 17 ([[/damage 4d8 lightning]]).</p>",
